name: DIVORCE CLICKBAIT
description: Creeper! Aww man. so we back in the mine. Got our pickaxe swinging from side to side, side side to side. This task a grueling one, gonna find some diamonds tonight night night, diamonds tonight. Heads up, you hear a sound, turn around and look up. It's the FBI. you haven't paid child support, and you will get the electric chair you degenerate. We are getting ice cream, and then coming to raid your house you idiot. Delete this, right now. Delete your child from existence, you dumb yee yee lookin haircut go to McDonald's and never come back. We're divorcing. Im taking the kids. Bye...
